* **Section 1 (Left):**  Consists of five orange/coral-colored cylindrical blocks, each supporting a stack of two green rectangular blocks.  There are two layers of green blocks in each stack.  The green blocks are arranged horizontally.

* **Section 2 (Right):** Composed of two yellow rectangular blocks stacked vertically to form a double-sided structure.  The structure has two layers with one yellow block stacked on top of the other.

There are a total of 7 blocks in the structure (5 orange/coral cylinders + 2 green rectangles + 2 yellow rectangles).  It has 3 layers (2 layers of green, and 1 layer of yellow).
